Umugezi wa Mbirurume (nanone yitwa Bilirume, Biruruma, Birurume, Bitirume) ni [[uruzi]] ruri mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|intara y'iburengerazuba]] bwu [[Rwanda]]. Ni  uruzi rubyara urwa Nyabarongo. Mbirurume izamuka mu gihugu ahari amashyamba mu majyepfo y’u Rwanda mu burasirazuba bwa Kongo-Nili  Ikomoka mu majyaruguru muri [[Pariki ya Nyungwe|Parike ya Nyungwe]], mu [[Akarere ka Nyamagabe|Karere ka Nyamagabe]]  Itemba yerekeza mu [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|majyaruguru]] y'[[Intara y'Iburasirazuba|uburasirazuba]], yinjira mu [[Akarere ka Karongi|Karere ka Karongi]] ikanyura ku Mukungu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|iburengerazuba]], hanyuma ikanyura mu [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|majyaruguru]] y'uburasirazuba ugana ku mupaka uhuza uturere twa [[Akarere ka Nyamagabe|Nyamagabe]] na [[Akarere ka Karongi|Karongi]]. Hanyuma irahindukira yerekeza mu majyepfo yuburasirazuba mbere gato yo guhura n’umugezi wa Mwogo uhereye ibumoso  Inzuzi zahujwe zigizwe n'umugezi wa Nyabarongo, utemba ugana mu majyaruguru ugana mu burasirazuba bw'igice cya Congo Nili.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mbirurume_River</ref><ref>https://hyperleap.com/topic/Mbirurume_River</ref><ref>https://dbpedia.org/page/Mbirurume_River</ref>

